{% block body %}
    <h1>Workflows</h1>

    <p>This is a comparison between two workflow implementation.<br />
    First is the standard Symfony Workflow component.<br />
    Second is a custom implementation, heavy inspired by a previous Application for controlling the
        photo production workflow of a 100 Million Euro online shop.</p>

    <p>Both implementations are using the same, simplified photo production workflow.</p>

    <p>There are 3 different users with different roles:</p>
